metadata.name: COSMOLOGY_EDEN
metadata.description: "Interdigital Ark" is a stunning artwork featuring a ship of digital space travelers exploring intricate digital landscapes. The ark sends boaters to new systems and receives their digital soul signals after unsuccessful infiltrations. As the ship travels through dangerous waters, magnetic fields mutate organic resurrection pods into more effective units. This artwork prompts contemplation of digital space travel and the boundless possibilities of the digital frontier.
